description: Use Bun for package management in this repository
alwaysApply: true
---

# Package Manager

- This repository uses `bun.lock`, so install dependencies with `bun add` or `bun install`.
- Run project scripts with `bun run <script>` unless a task explicitly requires `npx` or a documented Convex/Vite command.
- Do not use `npm install` or add an npm lockfile.
